    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=jzcv61xclq]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jzcv61xclq]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ay36vm62e6]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ay36vm62e6]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=bkn7vzcjnk]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=bkn7vzcjnk]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=py3cfq96tj]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=py3cfq96tj]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=v6resqdnvk]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=v6resqdnvk]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"TextureGif.gif\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/TextureGif.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755877353201&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/TextureGif.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755877353201&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"540\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567279715\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"TextureGif.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567509003\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"21\" data-media-id=\"a9264aef-532d-4510-be7a-e4c55f512894\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/TextureGif.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755877353201&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/TextureGif.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755877353201&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p>The texturing stage is one that I really enjoy and a stage where I can really add my own art style to a character, prop, or vehicle that I&rsquo;m working on.</p><p>I decided to use Substance Painter for my texturing.  I usually use Mari, but as I had set myself a 3-week deadline on this image, I already had some presets I&rsquo;d made from a different project that I knew could get me up and texturing faster.</p><p /><p>Before I started texturing, I had a few questions to answer. </p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"py3cfq96tj\">How old is the truck?</span></strong></p><p>I knew it wasn&rsquo;t brand new.  It had a life before it was converted, so it had been driven around town for many years.  It wasn&rsquo;t beaten up, but needed to feel used and old(ish)</p><p>In texturing, I knew the best way to demonstrate its age was to add wear, stains, and patina to the main paint.</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"v6resqdnvk\">Clean or Dirty?</span></strong></p><p>In my mind, the truck had to chase UFOs wherever they might go, so it needed to look like it had been driven both on roads and over dirt, too.  </p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ay36vm62e6\">What was the primary color the van had been repainted in?</span></strong></p><p>I went through a few colors, but after looking at some refs (and also a green van that drove past me one day), I decided on an army/camo green.  It feels like the right color and suits the van well.  The green paint gave it a rugged look that I was going for.</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"jzcv61xclq\">How can I show a bit of its past life?</span></strong></p><p>Knowing it was an ice cream van before, I wanted to give a hint at its past.  I decided to add an ice cream logo under the green paint and to remove some of the paint to provide the viewer with a faint glimpse of its previous life.</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"bkn7vzcjnk\">What text/decals can I use to amplify the story?</span></strong></p><p>Plus, as anyone who knows me and my art, I love a good sticker (or 100).  Adding text, adverts, and stickers to the van will help give it more of a story.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"STICKERS.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/STICKERS.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755874460599&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=452\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/STICKERS.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755874460599&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1191\" data-width=\"2000\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567509055\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"STICKERS.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567509003\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"21\" data-media-id=\"f5ae259e-29e7-4f8a-b176-dbae010cd833\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/STICKERS.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755874460599&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=904 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/STICKERS.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755874460599&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=452 1x\" /></span><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Painter2.png\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756393632504&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=193\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/Painter2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756393632504&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1044\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"576356355\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Painter2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567509003\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"21\" data-media-id=\"98eb800a-7d98-4a7e-babb-693d42e73777\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756393632504&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=386 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756393632504&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=193 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Painter3.png\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter3.png?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1756393638443&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=193\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/Painter3.png?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1756393638443&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1044\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"576094211\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Painter3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567509003\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"21\" data-media-id=\"df5af60d-65ba-4738-a50e-d4abbdbd9f36\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter3.png?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1756393638443&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=386 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter3.png?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1756393638443&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=193 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Painter1.png\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter1.png?version=4&amp;modificationDate=1756393671720&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=193\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/Painter1.png?version=4&amp;modificationDate=1756393671720&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1044\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"575963142\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Painter1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567509003\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"21\" data-media-id=\"7b2756da-c3dc-4550-bbfb-d52c63730cc1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter1.png?version=4&amp;modificationDate=1756393671720&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=386 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter1.png?version=4&amp;modificationDate=1756393671720&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=193 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Painter4.png\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter4.png?version=6&amp;modificationDate=1756393680033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=193\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/Painter4.png?version=6&amp;modificationDate=1756393680033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1044\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"576421890\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Painter4.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567509003\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"21\" data-media-id=\"a07f58c6-f65c-4994-a162-cba037181a02\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter4.png?version=6&amp;modificationDate=1756393680033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=386 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/Painter4.png?version=6&amp;modificationDate=1756393680033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=193 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PresetBrowser.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/PresetBrowser.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756394093633&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=497\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/PresetBrowser.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756394093633&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1344\" data-width=\"2054\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"576028678\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PresetBrowser.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567509003\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"21\" data-media-id=\"f77ac51e-495e-4804-96f9-8c472c4f58f9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/PresetBrowser.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756394093633&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=994 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/PresetBrowser.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756394093633&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=497 1x\" /></span><p /><p>Having decided to texture the van in Substance Painter, I was able to utilize the highly useful RenderMan Preset Browser, a material and lighting preset library that ships with RenderMan.</p><p>It is also a panel in Substance Painter that, with a single click, lets me quickly and easily export my materials directly from Painter into a RenderMan-compliant DCC.</p><p>It&rsquo;ll do all the manual work for me, which is a real timesaver.  It&rsquo;ll export .exr files for all channels in Painter for any or all selected materials, then convert those texture files to RenderMan&rsquo;s .tex format.  </p><p>Once it has those files, it will create a preset and create a shading network, all ready for me to load into Solaris (or Blender, Maya, Katana, etc)</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><a href=\"/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/VanTurntable_v01.mov?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762680518265&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760\">VanTurntable_v01.mov</a></span><p /><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><a href=\"/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/CrossingTurntable_v01.mov?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762678769416&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760\">CrossingTurntable_v01.mov</a></span><p /><hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757348276036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567509003/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757348276036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"100\" data-width=\"100\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"588939286\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567509003\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"21\" data-media-id=\"5c873f85-ef92-418c-bbdd-eb21c0b9f693\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757348276036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567509003/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757348276036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
